author: @adamurbanowski5794
text: Using the recent pull of data today, Yahoo have made a couple of changes to the naming of fields. Therefore field names in the Gather/DF statements need to change. 'Net Income Avl to Common ' becomes 'Net Income Avi to Common' and 'Shares Short (as of' becomes 'Shares Short ('. Without these changes you'll always get N/As for each stock so the NO_NA file will be empty.
